{"tid":1261102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗總唔衝得 律政衝得喇掛？","createTime":"2019-06-27T05:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:32:59.000Z","uid":256678,"like":555,"dislike":194,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"195d5083189983a4169b2c2085c624c29e7e2647","tid":1261102,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"跟本唔洗驚咩民意<br />\n去親邊 都有市民支持我地<br />\n唔好比啲一兩個建制post打巢我地嘅士氣！<br />\n<br />\n根本我地個勢從來無失過！<br />\n好多市民要返工 有屋企面照顧 但係又不滿哩個政府<br />\n其實佢地默默咁支持緊成個行動<br />\n今次得政府喺到話咩暴力之麻<br />\n街上面根本無市民屌啲後生<br />\n你地諗下2014？幾多人街頭罵戰 幾個占領區係咁比市民屌  仲記唔記得「你老母 那有錢」<br />\n今次完全無哩啲景像 反而一齊屌9個政府 差佬<br />\n<br />\n所以 唔洗驚政府同建制嘅輿論！"},{"pid":"3dd5144153e66cd54647d92bcc3edf5f316e27e4","tid":1261102,"uid":256678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db9a97adb09913885e57d0da96a830479c6d16af","tid":1261102,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5128c4ed57c83eeeba9260fff3a446f903840ee6","tid":1261102,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2932ff9262e5655c10fac2c13296251bcb52779","tid":1261102,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42876aef02d9eaea2267f8dbe32f8734cc395640","tid":1261102,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e53d7ebc3e6cfd4e609d15fef237ac232cba53b","tid":1261102,"uid":106870,"like":236,"dislike":4,"score":232,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"衝屎忽咩一千人都冇"},{"pid":"5df585ce6d8b8a31c49445db31d128fbb4d75bd0","tid":1261102,"uid":189151,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"如果衝律政，最大鑊會點先<br />\n警總就話搶槍上實彈啫，律政呢？"},{"pid":"83980e0dc7c304c2d878061